      "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/32/3/376/469",
      "text": [
        "۳۷۶. وَقَالَ (عليه ‏السلام): إِنَّ الْحَقَّ ثَقِيلٌ مَرِيءٌ وَإِنَّ الْبَاطِلَ خَفِيفٌ وَبِيءٌ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.sayed-ali-raza": [
          "376. Amīr al-mu’minīn, peace be upon him, said: Certainly, right is weighty and wholesome while wrong is light and epidemical."
        ]
      }
    }
